        dc:description           "Figure 4. Paraeutypella citricola (HMAS 290660) a-c. stromata on substrate; d. cross section of stroma; e. vertical section through stroma showing ostiolar necks and perithecia; f. ostiolar canal; g. peridium; h. paraphyses; i-k. asci; l-n. ascospores; o. germinating ascospore; p, q. culture on PDA after 6 weeks from above and below. Scale bars: 500 µm (b-d), 200 µm (e-g), 20 µm (g - l), 5 µm (m-o)." ;
